---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Teaching - Zeyu Li"
  description="Teaching experience and academic mentorship"
>
  <h1>Teaching</h1>
  <p class="page-intro">
    My teaching experience includes courses in materials science, chemistry, and biotechnology, 
    as well as mentoring graduate and undergraduate students.
  </p>

  <section class="teaching-section">
    <h2>Courses Taught</h2>
    <div class="course-list">
      <article class="course-item">
        <h3>Introduction to Materials Science</h3>
        <p class="course-meta">Undergraduate Level • Fall 2023</p>
        <p>
          Comprehensive introduction to the fundamental concepts of materials science, 
          covering structure-property relationships, processing, and characterization techniques.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="course-item">
        <h3>Advanced Biomaterials</h3>
        <p class="course-meta">Graduate Level • Spring 2024</p>
        <p>
          Advanced topics in biomaterials design, synthesis, and applications in 
          medical devices and tissue engineering.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="course-item">
        <h3>Laboratory Methods in Materials Research</h3>
        <p class="course-meta">Undergraduate Level • Fall 2022</p>
        <p>
          Hands-on laboratory course covering essential characterization techniques 
          including microscopy, spectroscopy, and mechanical testing.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <h2>Mentorship</h2>
    <p>
      I have had the privilege of mentoring several graduate and undergraduate students 
      in their research projects, helping them develop critical thinking skills and 
      advance their scientific careers.
    </p>
  </section>

  <style>
    h1 {
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    }

    .page-intro {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
      max-width: 800px;
    }

    .teaching-section h2 {
      margin-top: var(--spacing-2xl);
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
      color: var(--color-text);
    }

    .course-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--spacing-xl);
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
    }

    .course-item {
      padding: var(--spacing-lg);
      background: var(--color-surface);
      border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }

    .course-item h3 {
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
      color: var(--color-text);
    }

    .course-meta {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--color-text-muted);
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    }

    .course-item p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
      color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
